metadata.name: Disadvantages
metadata.description:
We all have defects. Weaknesses. Shortcomings. 
And we often hide them by lying. 

People want to look better than they are and I don’t just mean in a physical way. It’s our reality that sometimes we all wear masks and try to appear better. 

I don’t know can we live in a world where everyone will be honest. But I‘m trying to avoid lies and just be myself. 

What about you?
